WkMCP — NOTICE
=======================

This project is a multi-component distribution with a different license per
component. The shipped Desktop Extension bundle (`.mcpb`) is marked GPL-3.0 in
`manifest.json` because it contains the daemon, which links GPL-3.0-licensed
WolvenKit libraries. The MIT-licensed MCP server source is kept out of the
copyleft by a process boundary (see "Why two processes" below).

